      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since the day I got it! It looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot, with zero scratches or dents to be found. It runs like a dream and is ready for your next big road trip. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and see it for yourself!",
