    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example of the S54-powered legend. Featuring the high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, the mechanical integrity is superlative. The VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and rod bearing shells have been replaced as preventative maintenance. Subframe reinforcement has been completed to ensure chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagement, paired with the factory variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory depth with no discernible imperfections. This is a turn-key, investment-quality icon for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
