    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This car has been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled, preserving its deep, mirror-like factory finish without a single stone chip or swirl mark in sight. Step inside to find an interior that remains indistinguishable from the day it left the showroom; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any wear on the bolsters, and the cabin still retains that distinctive new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a full, documented service history with every maintenance milestone performed ahead of schedule. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, showing no signs of leaks or age. With incredibly low mileage and a flawless history, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a pristine example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
